description: Last season ended with Rick and our group kneeling helplessly before Negan and his group. What Negan does will haunt those who survive forever.
name: The Day Will Come When You Won't Be
Last One Out of Beach City

deck: Supergirl and the DEO are assigned to protect the President
description: Supergirl and the DEO are assigned to protect the President when an attack on her causes alien vs. human rights in National City to heat up. Alex investigates the case with Maggie Sawyer while Kara fears Mon-El may be responsible.
name: Welcome to Earth

deck: Mad Hatter sets his eyes on his next victims.
description: Mad Hatter sets his eyes on his next victims, forcing Jim Gordon to make some tough decisions. Meanwhile, Penguin and Nygma's relationship evolves, and a familiar face comes back into Nygma's life.
name: Mad City: Follow the White Rabbit

description: Robbie’s shocking story on how he became Ghost Rider is finally discovered as Coulson and his team’s lives hang in the balance.
name: The Good Samaritan

description: Barry lets Jesse tag along when a new meta human known as Mirror Master shows up and teams with his old partner Top to find Snart and settle a score. Jesse disobeys one of Barry's orders during the pursuit, resulting in disastrous consequences.
name: The New Rogues

deck: Oliver and Lyla team up on a secret mission for Diggle
description: Oliver and Lyla team up on a secret mission for Diggle. Felicity finds out and disapproves of the plan and opts to stay behind. When Tobias Church launches a deadly assault against the city, Felicity must decide if she wants to send the recruits out sans the Green Arrow.
name: Penance

description: Nate and Ray accidentally land in Feudal Japan after Nate discovers he has powers. Sara convinces Vixen that Rory is not a murderer, so they all agree to help Nate master his powers and defend the Japanese village from the Shogun and his army of samurai warriors. In the meantime, Jax and Stein find a secret compartment on the ship when they stay behind to fix it.
name: Shogun

description: Local teens, including the sheriff's daughter Lacey, raise hell when they steal the Delta from Brock's house. Ash and his best buddy Chet devise a plan to throw a party at the bar, lure the thieves in, and get the Delta and the Necronomicon back.
name: Last Call

description: Ash goes on the hunt for his beloved Delta, but becomes the hunted. Ruby and Kelly engage in a battle royale with the evil spawn while Pablo suffers from a new Necronomicon condition.
name: DUI

description: While the Hoenn region rejoices after avoiding meteoric destruction, reporter Gabby and her cameraman Ty uncover the story of a lifetime.
name: The Scoop

description: Late at night, a young traveler and her Chansey lose their way in Eterna Forest. They soon stumble upon a house, but what waits inside?
name: The Old Chateau
Beast Boy's St. Patrick's Day Luck and It's Bad
The Teen Titans Go Easter Holiday Classic
Batman v Teen Titans: Dark Injustice

description: Following a number of familiar faces, we are introduced to a new well-established community that seems too good to be true.
name: The Well

deck: Jim Gordon gets led on a psychedelic trip
description: After coming in contact with a substance by the hand of Mad Hatter, Jim Gordon gets led on a psychedelic trip and must confront his past, present and future. Meanwhile, Penguin struggles with Nygma's new relationship.
name: Red Queen

deck: Supergirl tries to stop an alien fight club
description: Supergirl tries to stop an alien fight club run by Roulette, while Hank gets to know M'Gann.
name: Survivors

deck: Caitlin visits her mother to help her
description: Caitlin visits her mother to help her understand her growing meta-human powers; Barry tries to convince Julian to let him help investigate a new meta-human attacking Central City.
name: Monster

description: When Cindy comes home from a trip to the mountains with photographs of UFOs, Andrea and Rick return with her to investigate.
name: The Lights of Mystery Mountain

description: Isis must solve the mystery of stolen diamonds, and one of Mrs. Thomass students fathers maybe involved.
name: Spots of the Leopard

description: Isis attempts to break up a ring of car thieves operating in town.
name: Fool's Dare

description: A student in need of money to buy a car, steals a device from Andrea that creates an impenetrable force field and sells it to a local crime boss. Isis goes in pursuit when she discovers the device has developed a dangerous radioactive leak.
name: The Sound of Silence

description: One of Andrea's students uses a geology field trip to avoid the chores his father assigned to him. Isis, and a foreign exchange student, teach him the meaning of responsibility.
name: Rockhound's Roost

description: A young boy distraught over the drowning death of his dog, gets into extreme danger and Isis acts quickly to try and save him.
name: Lucky

description: Someone, or something, huge is living in seclusion in the local mountains, and some of the students think it's the legendary monster "Bigfoot". Isis investigates.
name: Bigfoot

description: Tom, one of Rick's students, has trouble making friends, so to impress a new acquaintance, he shows him his dad's war souvenir handgun, which the new guy steals from Tom.
name: How to Find a Friend

description: Steve feels he has to draw attention to himself by showing off, which gets him into situations where Isis has to rescue him.
name: The Show-Off

description: Wayne is a new student at school who is described by the other students as a "hillbilly." Some boys who do not like Wayne plan to steal a rival school's raccoon mascot and frame Wayne as the thief. Wayne also gets in trouble for trying to stop the building of some houses in woods where some animals live.
name: The Outsider

description: Fred takes his runner-up finish in the Science Fair badly, and rushes off and almost drives his car off a cliff. After the near-accident, Andrea, Fred, and Dorothy drive to a ghost town, which is "haunted" by a trio of thieves using it as a hideout.
name: No Drums, No Trumpets

description: A overweight girl with low self-esteem steals Mr. Mason's boat for a publicity stunt and gets in so much danger that Isis has to call on superhero Captain Marvel to assist her.
name: Funny Gal

description: During a safety driving competition between boy and a beautiful girl, the boy cheats which eventually puts his life in grave danger, and Isis rushes to try and save him.
name: Girl Driver

description: A male student in Mr. Mason's scuba diving class does not like to follow safety rules and ends up getting trapped underwater as Isis rushes to try and save his life.
name: Scuba Duba

description: A teenage Hispanic girl makes innovative designs for flying model airplanes, but is hindered from competing by her brother and another boy who feel it's not a female's place to engineer planes. Isis knows they are wrong.
name: Dreams of Flight

deck: When Tobias Church captures and tortures one of Oliver's new recruits, Oliver must turn to an old friend
description: When Tobias Church captures and tortures one of Oliver's new recruits, Oliver must turn to an old friend, Christopher Chance AKA the Human Target, for help. Meanwhile, Felicity's worlds collide when Detective Malone joins the ACU.
name: Human Target

description: The Legends find themselves fighting for survival against Confederate zombies in the Civil War.
name: Abominations

deck: West and Gordon are tasked with guarding an Albanian princess, but when she is assassinated they discover she was an imposter.
description: The U.S. Secret Service tasks West and Gordon with guarding a visiting Albanian princess. West recognizes that the woman is an imposter, however before she can talk she is killed by a thrown knife.
name: Night of the Dancing Death

description: With the beginnings of a new universe laid out before him, Cyrus of Team Galactic faces extreme opposition. But aid arrives in an unusual form.
name: The New World

description: For the first time, the Turtles encounter something they cannot defeat...The Super Shredder!
name: The Super Shredder

description: A new group of survivors seem to have it all in their impressive community; however, there is a price.
name: The Cell

deck: Supergirl faces a ruthless new gang
description: Supergirl faces a ruthless new gang that's been given new alien technology by Cadmus.
name: Crossfire

description: Captain Barnes begins to feel the effects of a recent incident and starts to go mad. Meanwhile Nygma is out of his depth in his relationship with Isabella, and Carmine Falcone throws his son Mario and Leslie Tompkin's an engagement party.
name: Blood Rush

description: Felicity and Curtis learn that Prometheus' victims have a mysterious link to Oliver's past that could upend his new team.
name: So It Begins

description: The Legends trace a time quake to the White House during Ronald Reagan's presidency and discover that Damien Darhk is a Senior Adviser.
name: Compromised

description: The remnants of Team Galactic have awakened Heatran deep within Stark Mountain. Who can stop their burning ambitions from erupting into catastrophe?
name: The Magma Stone

description: Andrea helps her blind student develop self-confidence by teaching him to ride a horse.
name: Seeing Eye Horse

description: Isis saves Hope, a habitual hitchhiker, from a potentially fatal automobile accident and warns her not to continue hitching rides.
name: The Hitchhiker

description: Rudy tries to make himself popular by endlessly pulling practical jokes, including one that causes an emergency in the chemistry lab that endangers a student.
name: The Class Clown

description: A female cheerleader tries to get rid of her competition by cheating on a written exam, then attempts to frame another cheerleader by planting the stolen answers in her books.
name: The Cheerleader

description: Julie is reluctant to let her friends meet her father because of his "old-world ways."
name: Year of the Dragon

description: Detective Andrea and her students are hard on the case to prove Rick's innocence.
name: And Now You Don't

description: The remaining members of the group try to keep it together in Alexandria, however they receive a sobering visit.
name: Service

deck: Alex tells the truth about her self to kara
description: The Guardian arrives to lend a hand when an alien parasite drains Supergirl of her power. Mon-El contemplates his motives when he considers a new career. Alex faces a new reality.
name: Changing

deck: Ivy leads Selina and Bruce to trouble when she reveals her identity.
description: Gordon and Bullock become suspicious of Barnes and go through evidence of a murder at Lee and Mario's engagement party. Nygma goes to Penguin when he doesn't hear from Isabella. Ivy leads Selina and Bruce to trouble when she reveals her identity.
name: The Executioner

deck: Wally  is getting closer to take back his  power
description: Wally has visions of being Kid Flash, so Barry must tell him about what happened in Flashpoint to keep him safe.
name: Shade

description: With the loss of half the team, the remaining members search for answers as the clock counts down for Ghost Rider.
name: Deals with Our Devils

deck: a new vigilante  in town who is he
description: Oliver discovers there's a new vigilante in Star City when the bodies of two criminals are dropped at the SCPD. In flashbacks, Oliver faces Konstantin Kovar.
name: Vigilante

description: The Legends find Jonah Hex in trouble with his arch-nemesis Quentin Turnbull when they arrive in the Old West.
name: Outlaw Country

description: With the ascension of their king and the fall of the Pokémon League, Team Plasma is poised to take control—until the Gym Leaders arrive!
name: The Uprising

description: Saddled with grief and surrounded by enemies, members of the group try to find safety at the Hilltop before it's too late.
name: Go Getters

description: Donatello becomes concerned and decides to test April, only to discover that her psychic abilities are rapidly growing in power.
name: The Power Inside Her

description: The Turtle team hunts for their Sensei, but soon realizes they are being hunted as well.
name: Darkest Plight

description: The Dark Energem creates a black hole that takes the Rangers back in time, as they must go to a prehistoric age for their final showdown with Sledge and Fury.
name: End of Extinction

deck: An alien entity stirs up conflict between the Enterprise and a Klingon spaceship.
description: The Enterprise answers a distress call from a colony on Beta XII-A. When they arrive the colony has vanished. Soon after they are taken prisoner by a hostile band of Klingons who claim they have been attacked by the Enterprise.
name: Day of the Dove

deck: Cyborg Superman wants to kill supergirl
description: Supergirl comes face-to-face with Cyborg Superman when she attempts to save Mon-El from Cadmus.
name: The Darkest Place

deck: Jim comes to help Lee and Mario
description: A threat to Lee and Mario is exposed on the eve of their rehearsal dinner and Falcone comes to Jim for help. Meanwhile, Nygma plans his revenge and Bruce learns more about the Court of Owls.
name: Time Bomb

description: Proper Japanese Title: ザマスの野望　語られる恐怖の『人間０計画』(Zamasu no Yabō　Katarareru Kyōfu no “Ningen Zero Keikaku”)
name: Zamasu's Ambition - The Awful "Zero Mortal Plan" Is Revealed"

deck: Caitlin  goes in  to find  Alchemy
description: The team is in for a shock as Caitlin is forced to reveal her Killer Frost powers - but she is not the only one with a secret.
name: Killer Frost

description: Proper Japanese Title: 世界はオレが守る！トランクス怒りの超パワー炸裂！！(Sekai wa Ore ga Mamoru! Torankusu Ikari no Sūpā Pawā Sakuretsu!!)
name: I'll Protect the World! Trunks' Furious Super Power Explodes!!

description: Proper Japanese Title: サイヤ人の細胞を汚すな！ベジータの壮絶バトル開演！！(Saiya-jin no Saibō o Kegasu na! Bejīta no Sōzetsu Batoru Kaien!!)
name: Don't Disrespect Saiyan Cells! Vegeta's Heroic Battle Begins!!

description: Gym Leader Drayden prepares to defend Opelucid City against Team Plasma, but the true nature of their plans will chill him to his very core.
name: The Frozen World

description: Proper Japanese Title: 崇めよ！讃えよ！合体ザマス爆誕！！(Agame yo! Tatae yo! Gattai Zamasu Bakutan!!)
name: Revere Him! Praise Him! Fusion Zamasu's Explosive Birth!!

description: Proper Japanese Title: 最後の審判か！？絶対神の究極の力(Saigo no Shinpan ka!? Zettai Shin no Kyūkyoku no Pawā)
name: Final Judgement?! The Supreme God’s Ultimate Power
